snippet.title: Aquaman Spinoff "The Trench" Cancelled Because of Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Aquaman Spinoff "The Trench" Cancelled Because of Amber Heard.
The drama between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp has had a lot of consequences for themselves, the people close to them, their careers but also for the movies that they are a part of! 
Having a lead role involved in so serious issues is not something most companies want and therefore both Amber Heard and Johnny Depp have lost multiple roles because of this. But this has also hurt the movies themselves and the new upcoming Aquaman movie "The Trench" has most likely been cancelled because that Amber Heard couldn't be a part of it.
